nodes.text: Shaak kebab was a kebab dish made from shaaks, a species native to the planet Naboo. It could be purchased in a bar on a desert world for credits in 9 ABY. The dish was listed on the bar's menu in Aurebesh among the other foods sold there.

Shaak kebab was mentioned on a menu featured in "Chapter 16: The Rescue," the eighth and final episode of the second season of The Mandalorian and the sixteenth episode of the series overall. The episode aired on December 18, 2020.
